text: Jill De Bruyn (born 13 December 1993) is a Luxembourger footballer who plays as a midfielder for Dames Ligue 1 club SC Ell and the Luxembourg women's national team. ==International career== De Bruyn made her senior debut for Luxembourg on 3 March 2018 during a 1–7 friendly loss to Morocco. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers
